  "3068710": {
    "name": "维度启程",
    "steam_appid": 3068710,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3068710/extras/bbb48f0f4132e74c03c504825fc45c13.avif?t=1765362714\" width=720 height=330 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《维克托里亚》中，你将扮演好奇的二维生物皮洛，穿梭于悬浮于不断变幻维度中的浩瀚远古遗迹。在这超现实世界中，你将切换二维与三维视角，操控重力开辟新路，破解颠覆传统空间认知的烧脑谜题。途中你将邂逅形形色色的奇异角色，他们各自对这个世界有着独特见解，并将指引你踏上追寻失落记忆真相的征程。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3068710/extras/e22149c6d56c503209fa7062d71b24c9.avif?t=1765362714\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3068710/extras_big/e22149c6d56c503209fa7062d71b24c9.avif?t=1765362714 width=800 height=160 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你醒来时毫无记忆，不知自己是谁，也不知为何来到此地，唯独察觉到这个世界正以不可思议的方式回应着你：平面旋转，重力弯曲，墙壁化作地面。每向前一步，便在变幻的几何结构深处，抽丝剥茧般揭开新的谜团线索。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3068710/extras/820e489b535ac9f2d39b94e860772522.avif?t=1765362714\" width=780 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3068710/extras/66f81b5b8002c3af48ffb7c53fe0410d.avif?t=1765362714\" width=1200 height=229 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>扭曲与转折，从二维视角探索超现实3D世界</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3068710/extras/da2065c924536b0cca3e7de1fa5150c3.poster.avif?t=1765362714\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3068710/extras/da2065c924536b0cca3e7de1fa5150c3.webm?t=1765362714\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3068710/extras/da2065c924536b0cca3e7de1fa5150c3.mp4?t=1765362714\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3068710/extras/6a6d4589a8a8bf8b9ec901c80893302b.avif?t=1765362714\" width=1200 height=229 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>发掘隐秘的记忆碎片与失落的历史</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3068710/extras/e59fb283c924b254cd6add3e8bb9e052.poster.avif?t=1765362714\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3068710/extras/e59fb283c924b254cd6add3e8bb9e052.webm?t=1765362714\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3068710/extras/e59fb283c924b254cd6add3e8bb9e052.mp4?t=1765362714\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3068710/extras/77186d361d47c8f7184f178c2977ad54.avif?t=1765362714\" width=1200 height=229 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>操控重力，在空间中开辟不可能的通路</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3068710/extras/bdeaa37e2a55de8183272ca480f268d2.poster.avif?t=1765362714\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3068710/extras/bdeaa37e2a55de8183272ca480f268d2.webm?t=1765362714\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3068710/extras/bdeaa37e2a55de8183272ca480f268d2.mp4?t=1765362714\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3068710/extras/77b15fe6a3fd882c30f54b5fb3571111.avif?t=1765362714\" width=1200 height=229 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>在枢纽区域破解元谜题，推进游戏进程</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3068710/extras/d20ba9d56fe55043d2429bb3dd1a3ed4.poster.avif?t=1765362714\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3068710/extras/d20ba9d56fe55043d2429bb3dd1a3ed4.webm?t=1765362714\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3068710/extras/d20ba9d56fe55043d2429bb3dd1a3ed4.mp4?t=1765362714\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3068710/extras/75e2919b412cc185cf8e4543c9729e9e.avif?t=1765362714\" width=780 height=150 /></span></p>",
